This year for nurses week, we recognize that work life balance is so hard for so many nurses. We understand you need to put your life first so you can thrive on and off the shift. 

We’re excited to announce a giveaway at the end of the week that supports this idea, and helps you be the best person and nurse you can be. Stay tuned!
